TEXT PROPERTIES:
1. Color
1. Color: colorname

2. Hexadecimal values (0-9, A-F)
 eg color: #FFFFFF;
 color #FFFFFF : White
      #000000: Black
      #FF0000: Red

shorthand for white = #FFF
              red = #F00
using shorthand not recommended

3. rgb color code (0-256):
eg - color: rgb(255, 0, 0); - red

4.rgba color code (0-256):
eg color: rgb(255, 0, 0, 0.6)

2. text-align (left, right, center, justify):
justify: aligning text according to its length

3.text-transform(uppercase, lowercase, capitalize):
Capitalize only uses uppercase for initials

4.text-decoration(overline, underline, line-through):

5. text-indent(px):
eg. text-indent: 5px

6. letter-spacing(px): Kerning

7. word-spacing(px): Space between two words

8.line-height(px): space between two lines

FONT PROPERTIES:

1. font-size(px/em):
eg/ font-size: 14px or 1em
em is responsive

2. font-family():
    e.g. font-family: Arial, Times new Roman
    The first available will be applied if neither available machines default font is used.

3. font-weight(bold, normal, 100, 200...700, bolder):
  default is normal, bold and normal available on machines

4. font-style(normal, italic):
  default normal.

